Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.79,0:00:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.04,0:01:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[rattling]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.50,0:01:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[door thuds]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.88,0:01:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] How many seconds has it been\Nsince you wrote down the first name?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.56,0:01:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thirty-five, 36, 37,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.98,0:01:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,thirty-eight, 39...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.44,0:01:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Near, looks like I win.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.78,0:01:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mikami] Forty!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.40,0:01:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,NEW WORLD
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.25,0:02:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[both shuddering]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.59,0:02:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.01,0:02:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.80,0:02:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been over a minute\Nand we haven't died!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.93,0:02:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I already tell you all\Nthat no one was gonna die?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.69,0:02:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mikami stammering] But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.23,0:02:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't they die?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.98,0:02:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[shuddering breathing]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.03,0:02:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mikami] God!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.49,0:02:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I did everything you told me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.82,0:02:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Rester, Gevanni, take him now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.95,0:02:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mikami yelling frantically]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.62,0:02:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Gevanni, the notebook, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.05,0:02:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If you didn't believe me earlier,\Nthen see for yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.92,0:03:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,KANZO MOGI TOUTA MATSUDA\NHIDEKI IDE SHUICHI AIZAWA
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.63,0:03:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I can confirm that the first four names\Nare definitely the real names
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.14,0:03:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,of the SPK members.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.72,0:03:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The second four are the names\Nof your team.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.97,0:03:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The only name that hasn't\Nbeen written down...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.06,0:03:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,is Light Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.73,0:03:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[snarling]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.31,0:03:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] If that weren't enough,\NMikami also addressed you as "God,"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.82,0:03:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and said he did what you asked him to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.70,0:03:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light breathes shakily]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.57,0:03:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a trap! This whole thing is a setup!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all part of Near's plan\Nto frame me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it a little odd that no one died
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.29,0:03:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,after having their name\Nwritten in the notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.29,0:03:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This proves it's a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.75,0:03:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.17,0:03:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.22,0:03:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe I already told you\Nthat no one would die
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.59,0:03:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-because I modified the notebook.\N-[Light gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You-- [panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[huffs] That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.27,0:03:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a setup. I don't know this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.94,0:03:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[begins sobbing]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.40,0:04:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Light, it's too late to deny it.\NYou know Near has won.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.91,0:04:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a moment ago, you were saying,\N"It looks like I win."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.45,0:04:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How much more of a confession\Ndo we need?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.71,0:04:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.38,0:04:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.14,0:04:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.35,0:04:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[yelling in panic]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.56,0:04:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Light Yagami. L. Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.99,0:04:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over. You've lost the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.54,0:04:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a moment ago,\Nyou proclaimed your victory,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.21,0:04:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,expecting us all to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And to tell the truth,\Nyou might've actually won.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.54,0:05:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And I would've lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.01,0:05:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We ended up doing exactly\Nwhat you expected us to,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and altered the fake notebook\Nin Mikami's possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.35,0:05:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,However, when I said before\Nthat we had modified the notebook,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.39,0:05:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in fact referring\Nto the real notebook as well as the fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.19,0:05:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.69,0:05:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We only switched part\Nof the fake notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.15,0:05:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But as for the real one,\Nwe replaced the entire thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.15,0:05:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This notebook here\Nis actually the real one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.53,0:05:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] No! Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.87,0:05:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] We used the same kind\Nof pen that Mikami used,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.37,0:05:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,copied his handwriting perfectly,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and made both the inside\Nand the outside of our fake
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.33,0:05:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,look exactly like the original.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.46,0:05:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Gevanni was able to do it\Nin a single night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.92,0:05:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, since I had touched\Nthe real notebook before coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been able to see the Shinigami\Nas well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.97,0:05:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ah...\N-[Aizawa] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.81,0:05:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure to meet you,\NMr. Shinigami. I'm Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:06:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[cackles] Nice to meet you too.\NMy name is Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.36,0:06:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] He can talk to Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He can see him, so that means...\Nit must be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.36,0:06:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Some of the edges\Nof this notebook's pages are torn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.07,0:06:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, if someone's name was written\Non a ripped off piece of paper,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.24,0:06:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,would they still die?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. Of course they would.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.50,0:06:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.79,0:06:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you were able to use that\Nto your advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.42,0:06:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how many times you deceived us\Nwith this, and how many people you killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.76,0:06:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Light Yagami, you are Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.27,0:06:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] This has gotta be a trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.44,0:06:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Or could it be that Mikami's betrayed me\Nsomehow?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.81,0:06:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Near] You're mistaken.\N-[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.61,0:06:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This was all thanks to Mello.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.32,0:06:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe if I explain this much,\Nyou'll begin to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.74,0:06:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] What? Mello?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.66,0:06:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take a look at this page\Nof the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.66,0:06:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.87,0:06:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,KIYOMI TAKADA SUICIDE\NBURNS TO DEATH
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.16,0:06:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Takada's name is in the notebook!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.71,0:07:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting] I was the one who killed her,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.62,0:07:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but her death was written there\Njust one minute later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.58,0:07:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,JANUARY 26 2:33 PM
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.38,0:07:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean Mikami\Ndid the same thing I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.09,0:07:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,God! You told me you couldn't move freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.22,0:07:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to make sure Takada\Nwas taken care of!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.93,0:07:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that my duty to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.68,0:07:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.64,0:07:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave you strict orders not to make\Nany unnecessary movements until today!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.06,0:07:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.31,0:07:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,On the 26th,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,right after Takada's kidnapping\Nwas broadcast on the news,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.32,0:07:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikami went to the bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.28,0:07:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been trailing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew he went to the bank\Neveryone month on the 25th.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.74,0:07:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it was odd for someone so methodical\Nto go to the bank twice in two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.25,0:07:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I followed Mikami to the bank as he headed\Nfor the safe deposit boxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.04,0:07:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It was only at this time\Nthat he seemed concerned
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.59,0:07:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,whether someone was following him or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.71,0:07:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I got into his safe deposit box.\NInside was the real notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.47,0:07:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure enough, Takada's name had already\Nbeen written inside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.85,0:08:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Do you understand now,\NLight Yagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.10,0:08:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't realize\Nthat Mikami made a move on his own
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.65,0:08:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and wrote Takada's name in his notebook
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,because you had already killed her\Nusing a notebook clipping yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.32,0:08:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This was the event that made me consider\Nthe possibility of a fake notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.32,0:08:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We were able to stop you\Nthanks to the efforts of one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.58,0:08:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Mello who did it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[Lidner] Mello probably knew\Nwhat was going to happen all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.08,0:08:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mello] It can be resolved by having\Na name written in the notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.42,0:08:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.76,0:08:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mello] Well then, if I don't do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet Mello knew in his heart
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.22,0:08:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,that working by ourselves, neither of us\Nwould be able to attain our goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.98,0:08:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and surpass our mentor, L.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.06,0:08:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But together...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.23,0:08:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,together, we can stand with L.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.73,0:08:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Together, we can surpass L!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, acting as one,\Nwe face the Kira who defeated L,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.99,0:08:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and with solid evidence,\Nbeat him at his own game!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.20,0:09:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see you try and talk your way\Nout of this one... if you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.80,0:09:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light laughs softly]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.89,0:09:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughing intensifies]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.31,0:09:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughing maniacally]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.91,0:09:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.70,0:09:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.64,0:10:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I am Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And what can you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.98,0:10:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill me right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear this. I'm not only Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.33,0:10:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm also...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.91,0:10:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,God of the new world!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.83,0:10:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira has become law in the world\Nwe now live.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the one who's maintaining order.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.21,0:10:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I have become Justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.84,0:10:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The only hope for mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.18,0:10:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[snickers] Kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.10,0:10:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that really the right thing to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.19,0:10:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Since Kira's appearance six years ago,\Nwars have stopped
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.27,0:10:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and global crime rates have been\Nreduced by over 70 percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.19,0:11:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But, it's not enough.\NThis world is still rotten!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.36,0:11:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,With too many rotten people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.74,0:11:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody has to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,When I first got that notebook,\Nall those years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.46,0:11:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I had to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.67,0:11:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I was the only one who could!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I understood that killing people\Nwas a crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.43,0:11:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[glass shattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.72,0:11:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no other way!\NThe world had to be fixed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.43,0:11:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A purpose given to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.64,0:11:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Only I could do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.02,0:11:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Who else could have done it?\NAnd come this far?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.82,0:11:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Would they have kept going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.61,0:11:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The only one...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.32,0:11:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,who can create a new world... is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.21,0:11:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No. You're just a murderer, Light Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.88,0:12:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And this notebook is the deadliest\Nweapon of mass murder
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.09,0:12:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,in the history of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You yielded to the power\Nof the Shinigami and the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.81,0:12:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And you have confused yourself\Nwith a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, you're nothing more\Nthan a crazy serial killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.73,0:12:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.52,0:12:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing more and nothing less.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.38,0:12:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Useless fools.\NAs if they could ever understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:13:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's some food for thought.\NThat notebook you have,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and the one that Aizawa brought\Nfrom the Japanese Task Force Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.28,0:13:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they both real?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.66,0:13:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] What is he up to?\NIs he bluffing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.24,0:13:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] At the moment, only I know\Nwhere the real notebook is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.62,0:13:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you truly wanna defeat Kira,\Nas well as test the notebook
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.38,0:13:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,that Aizawa's carrying...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're gonna have to write down\Neither my name or Mikami's.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.60,0:13:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only way to see if it's real...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,or fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.36,0:13:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He's hidden a piece of the notebook!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.19,0:13:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.49,0:13:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.61,0:13:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.49,0:13:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsuda, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell do you think\Nyou're shooting at?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.08,0:13:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't screw with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.83,0:14:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it all for, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.17,0:14:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What about your dad?\NWhat the hell did he die for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.59,0:14:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[wheezing] My dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.68,0:14:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs] You mean Soichiro Yagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.18,0:14:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Matsuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.64,0:14:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,In this world, all those earnest people\Nlike him who fight for justice,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.06,0:14:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,they always lose. You want a world where\Npeople like that are made to be fools?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.65,0:14:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you understand, so kill the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.23,0:14:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You led your own father to his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.16,0:14:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And now he's gone, you call him a fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.83,0:14:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-His blood!\N-[Matsuda yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.58,0:14:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[gunshots]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.92,0:14:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'll kill him!\N-[Light gasping for air]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.42,0:14:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill him! He has to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.97,0:14:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[gunshot echoing]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.61,0:15:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.41,0:15:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Damn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.16,0:15:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.87,0:15:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikami! What are you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.38,0:15:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Write down their names!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.26,0:15:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Write them down! Kill them now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.93,0:15:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mikami breathing shakily]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.14,0:15:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mogi] It's finally over, isn't it Near?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.14,0:15:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[wheezing]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.60,0:15:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you Misa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Takada? [sobs]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.95,0:15:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[wheezing] Someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.91,0:16:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[sobbing] What do I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mikami screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.14,0:16:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikami!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.31,0:16:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mikami screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.27,0:16:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aikawa] Quick. Stop the bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.89,0:16:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[Gevanni] It's already too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.52,0:16:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be dead in a few seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.87,0:16:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.37,0:16:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.33,0:16:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He's getting away! Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.17,0:16:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Near] Mr. Aizawa!\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.59,0:16:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unlikely he has any more pieces\Nof the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.55,0:16:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And with those wounds,\Nhe's not going to go far.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:16:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll stop running soon,\Neven if we leave him alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.93,0:17:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. Near, I'm not gonna follow\Nyour orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.85,0:17:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.02,0:17:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well, then. I'll leave it up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.45,0:17:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light breathing shakily]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.57,0:17:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light begins sobbing]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.41,0:18:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.29,0:18:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] Well, Light,\Nit looks like you've lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.13,0:18:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember how, in the beginning,\Nwhen we first met,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.67,0:18:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you that I'd be the one\Nwriting your name in my notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.76,0:19:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That is part of the agreement
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.97,0:19:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,between a Shinigami who brings a notebook\Nto the human world...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.60,0:19:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and the first human who picks it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.52,0:19:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If they put you in prison,\Nwho knows when you'd die?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.69,0:19:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't wanna lie around waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.78,0:19:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.20,0:19:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.84,0:19:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It was good while it lasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.09,0:19:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We eased each other's boredom\Nfor quite a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.64,0:19:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Light, it's been interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.39,0:19:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,LIGHT YAGAMI
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.01,0:20:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[soft piano music playing]